txt.en: 'See here, postman, hold a minute. I'm wanting to see if you've any mail for me.'
'Good day postman, what post might you have for me?'
'Postman, I simply must know what mail you have for me!'
'What's this, a postman? Tell me, what mail have you for me?'
'Look there, a postman. Might you have any post for me?'
